---
title: Tangy Beyond Meat® Burgers with German-Style Potato Salad
description: Pan-fried, crispy, Beyond Meat® goodness! The crunchy pickles and savoury caramelized onions on this burger will take your meal to the next level. We've even chopped up some pickles to add zing to our classic potato salad. It's safe to say you won't miss the BBQ with this stovetop-friendly dinner!
